import React from 'react'
import Icon3 from '../../images/image3.svg'
import Icon4 from '../../images/image4.svg'
import Icon5 from '../../images/image5.svg'
import {
  ServicesContainer,
  ServicesH1,
  ServicesWrapper,
  ServicesCard,
  ServicesIcon,
  ServicesH2,
  ServicesP,
} from './ServicesElements'

const Services = () => {
  return (
    <ServicesContainer id="services">
      <ServicesH1>Why Multilingually</ServicesH1>
      <ServicesWrapper>
        <ServicesCard>
          <ServicesIcon src={Icon3} />
          <ServicesH2>Customized Learning</ServicesH2>
          <ServicesP>
            Choose from over a dozen highly qualified teachers for 1-on-1
            lessons based on your goals and interests.
          </ServicesP>
        </ServicesCard>
        <ServicesCard>
          <ServicesIcon src={Icon4} />
          <ServicesH2>Pay Per Lesson</ServicesH2>
          <ServicesP>
            On Multilingually you only pay per lesson and at the price that
            meets your budget. The price should not be an obstacle!
          </ServicesP>
        </ServicesCard>
        <ServicesCard>
          <ServicesIcon src={Icon5} />
          <ServicesH2>Anytime, Anywhere</ServicesH2>
          <ServicesP>
            Take online lessons at the time and place that suits you. We are
            flexible and always here to support you!
          </ServicesP>
        </ServicesCard>
      </ServicesWrapper>
    </ServicesContainer>
  )
}

export default Services
